				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">1. if you have suspend minion, suspend it and re-suspend when you arrive.
<br />

<br />
2. get spell: velocity, magician spell that casts a form of spirit of wolf on your pet.
<br />

<br />
3. before you arrive at your spot, wait a dozen seconds or so until you see your pet approach you.  now when you walk that last 100 feet to your arrival point, pet will be awfully close by.
<br />

<br />
-cc</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
