			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Even with Velocity, running at 100K horse speed (Cheetah, IIRC?) WILL leave your pet straggling at the rear, so keep summon companion memmed (or an item hot-keyed) or have another pet suspended.
<br />

<br />
Personally, I travel with a pocketed pet (Persistent Minion) and one tail-gating me. But around areas I don't know, I keep summon companion up or travel slow enough that Jibobaber keeps up.
<br />

<br />
Don't rely on Velocity to keep your pet near you. Pathing and just plain being twice as fast as gas-ball will separate you over significant distances.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=320122" target="_blank" class="postlink">Majishia Vie </a>
<br />
<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=827513" target="_blank" class="postlink">Fayth Vanquisher </a>
