				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I absolutely LOVE my 100K horse.
<br />
The only problem is....
<br />
I only have him on Jeradim, so when I'm travelling I always run because otherwise Bell wouldn't be able to keep up.  I can't quite bring myself to spend <span style="font-style: italic">another</span> 100K for him.  Perhaps when I have a couple more hundred thousand pp banked I will.
<br />
Now that I've had my taste of what it's like to be "rich" - I mean really rich...10K used to be rich, then 100K, but now I'd say that number is higher - I dont' like to go below 100K because then I'm getting low on funds hehe.  I still can't quite fathom though how people have like a millions of pp.  I guess the Ubers just have access to the better zones and hence the better loot and since they're raid geared they would never need anything that ever drops in like WoS for example so they can just sell everything and amass the cash.
<br />

